<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="description" content=""/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>Circle reading mode</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body{
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #5f6367;
      line-height: 1.75;
      background: #fff;
      font-family: "Lucida Grande", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;
    }
    .circle-about a{
      color: #5f6367;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .circle-about a:hover{
      color:#4974d4;
    }
    .circle-block{
      display: block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d9dce0;
    }
    .circle-share{
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d9dce0;
    }
    .circle-donate{
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="circle-about">
    <a target="_blank" class="circle-block" href="https://github.com/hewenguang/circle/issues">Question feedback</a>
    <a target="_blank" class="circle-block" href="https://ranhe.xyz/circle-usage/">Guide to use</a>
    <a target="_blank" class="circle-block" href="https://github.com/hewenguang/circle">View the source code on GitHub</a>
    <a target="_blank" class="circle-block" href="https://jq.qq.com/?_wv=1027&k=VVzeMjMK">QQ discussion group: 605710052</a>
    <a target="_blank" class="circle-block" href="mailto:wenguang.fe@gmail.com">For other matters, please contact email: wenguang.fe @ gmail.com</a>
    <div class="circle-share"></div>
    <p class="circle-donate">If circle does help you, why don't you buy me a drink ☕ To show encouragement and support 😄 </p>
    <p class="circle-donate"><img src="https://ranhe.xyz/post-images/donate.jpg" /></p>
  </div>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/social-share.js/1.0.16/css/share.min.css">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/social-share.js/1.0.16/js/social-share.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    socialShare('.circle-share', {
      url: 'https://ranhe.xyz/circle',
      title: '让网页赏心悦目、让阅读回归初心 - Circle 还你最纯粹的阅读体验，为你更好的阅读保驾护航',
      image: 'https://ranhe.xyz/post-images/1613019066732.png',
      description: '广告太多分散注意力、配色太丑不忍直视、字体太小看不清、排版太乱找不到正文，阅读真的需要这么困难吗？Circle 还你最纯粹的阅读体验，为你更好的阅读保驾护航',
      sites: ['wechat', 'qq', 'qzone', 'weibo', 'douban', 'linkedin', 'facebook', 'twitter', 'google'],
    });
  </script>
  <% if (site.customConfig.ga) { %>
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=<%= site.customConfig.ga %>"></script>
    <script>
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        function gtag() {dataLayer.push(arguments);}
        gtag('js', new Date());
        gtag('config', '<%= site.customConfig.ga %>');
    </script>
  <% } %>
</body>
</html>
